00:45:44.980 --> 00:45:46.920 align:middle line:90%
>> Hey.

00:45:46.920 --> 00:45:49.280 align:middle line:90%
Thanks.

00:45:49.280 --> 00:45:51.200 align:middle line:90%
>> You overworked yourself.

00:45:51.200 --> 00:45:52.700 align:middle line:84%
And your body
eventually catches up.

00:45:52.700 --> 00:45:54.450 align:middle line:90%
You know that.

00:45:54.450 --> 00:45:58.160 align:middle line:84%
>> You know, something happened
the day of the accident.

00:45:58.160 --> 00:45:59.540 align:middle line:90%
Something went off in my brain.

00:45:59.540 --> 00:46:01.460 align:middle line:90%
>> Give yourself a break.

00:46:01.460 --> 00:46:04.080 align:middle line:84%
It's only been a few weeks, and
you've had a lot to deal with.

00:46:04.080 --> 00:46:05.538 align:middle line:84%
And I don't just
mean the accident.

00:46:05.538 --> 00:46:11.534 align:middle line:90%


00:46:11.534 --> 00:46:12.530 align:middle line:90%
>> Sorry.

00:46:12.530 --> 00:46:22.490 align:middle line:90%


00:46:22.490 --> 00:46:25.478 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:46:25.478 --> 00:46:29.960 align:middle line:90%


00:46:29.960 --> 00:46:32.948 align:middle line:90%
[ELEVATOR RUNNING]

00:46:32.948 --> 00:46:40.916 align:middle line:90%


00:46:40.916 --> 00:46:43.904 align:middle line:90%
[DOOR OPENING]

00:46:43.904 --> 00:46:44.598 align:middle line:90%


00:46:44.598 --> 00:46:45.398 align:middle line:90%
>> Hey.

00:46:45.398 --> 00:46:46.394 align:middle line:90%
>> I need to talk to you.

00:46:46.394 --> 00:46:47.194 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah?

00:46:47.194 --> 00:46:50.378 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:46:50.378 --> 00:47:26.234 align:middle line:90%


00:47:26.234 --> 00:47:28.724 align:middle line:90%
>> Leah.

00:47:28.724 --> 00:47:31.640 align:middle line:84%
I never felt anything
like this before.

00:47:31.640 --> 00:47:32.696 align:middle line:90%
>> You don't know me.

00:47:32.696 --> 00:47:36.887 align:middle line:84%
>> That doesn't
change how I feel.

00:47:36.887 --> 00:47:39.780 align:middle line:84%
>> Do you believe
in coincidences?

00:47:39.780 --> 00:47:42.230 align:middle line:90%
>> No.

00:47:42.230 --> 00:47:43.030 align:middle line:90%
>> I do.

00:47:43.030 --> 00:47:46.310 align:middle line:90%


00:47:46.310 --> 00:47:47.110 align:middle line:90%
I do.

00:47:47.110 --> 00:47:51.280 align:middle line:84%
And I think that
we met by accident

00:47:51.280 --> 00:47:53.410 align:middle line:84%
and that, given
the circumstances,

00:47:53.410 --> 00:47:57.970 align:middle line:90%
we're idealizing this, us.

00:47:57.970 --> 00:47:58.870 align:middle line:90%
Look.

00:47:58.870 --> 00:48:00.660 align:middle line:90%
I have to focus on my work.

00:48:00.660 --> 00:48:04.020 align:middle line:84%
I can't afford any
distractions right now.

00:48:04.020 --> 00:48:06.350 align:middle line:90%
>> Distraction?

00:48:06.350 --> 00:48:07.150 align:middle line:90%
Is that what I am?

00:48:07.150 --> 00:48:15.427 align:middle line:90%


00:48:15.427 --> 00:48:16.260 align:middle line:90%
Do you feel nothing?

00:48:16.260 --> 00:48:19.669 align:middle line:90%


00:48:19.669 --> 00:48:21.951 align:middle line:90%
>> We're different.

00:48:21.951 --> 00:48:22.905 align:middle line:90%
>> Are we?

00:48:22.905 --> 00:48:28.160 align:middle line:90%


00:48:28.160 --> 00:48:31.100 align:middle line:90%
>> I can't do this.

00:48:31.100 --> 00:48:34.180 align:middle line:84%
>> What were you doing that day,
the morning of the accident?

00:48:34.180 --> 00:48:35.650 align:middle line:90%
>> I was jogging.

00:48:35.650 --> 00:48:38.076 align:middle line:90%
>> Down at the pier, that early?

00:48:38.076 --> 00:48:40.390 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, I couldn't sleep.

00:48:40.390 --> 00:48:42.510 align:middle line:90%
>> See?

00:48:42.510 --> 00:48:46.030 align:middle line:84%
It's not a coincidence
that you and I met.

00:48:46.030 --> 00:48:47.808 align:middle line:84%
I'm standing here
because of you.

00:48:47.808 --> 00:48:51.800 align:middle line:90%


00:48:51.800 --> 00:48:55.250 align:middle line:90%
>> Look, I'm sorry.

00:48:55.250 --> 00:48:58.722 align:middle line:90%
[DOOR CLOSES]

00:48:58.722 --> 00:48:59.714 align:middle line:90%


00:48:59.714 --> 00:49:02.690 align:middle line:90%
[ELEVATOR RUNNING]

00:49:02.690 --> 00:49:09.138 align:middle line:90%


00:49:09.138 --> 00:49:12.610 align:middle line:90%
[THUNDER RUMBLES]

00:49:12.610 --> 00:49:17.074 align:middle line:90%


00:49:17.074 --> 00:49:20.546 align:middle line:90%
[SOUND OF WATER]

00:49:20.546 --> 00:49:24.018 align:middle line:90%
[SCREAMING]

00:49:24.018 --> 00:49:31.954 align:middle line:90%


00:49:31.954 --> 00:49:34.930 align:middle line:90%
[WATER RUNNING]

00:49:34.930 --> 00:49:59.234 align:middle line:90%


00:49:59.234 --> 00:50:00.226 align:middle line:90%
>> Here you go.

00:50:00.226 --> 00:50:05.330 align:middle line:90%


00:50:05.330 --> 00:50:08.060 align:middle line:84%
I suggest that,
through hypnosis, we

00:50:08.060 --> 00:50:10.730 align:middle line:84%
see if any memories
come up that can

00:50:10.730 --> 00:50:13.732 align:middle line:90%
help us understand your fears.

00:50:13.732 --> 00:50:16.190 align:middle line:84%
>> Dr. Anderson, I was hoping
that you would suggest a more

00:50:16.190 --> 00:50:18.470 align:middle line:90%
traditional approach.

00:50:18.470 --> 00:50:21.190 align:middle line:90%
>> I understand.

00:50:21.190 --> 00:50:23.470 align:middle line:84%
Hypnotherapy is an option
I'd like to explore

00:50:23.470 --> 00:50:24.565 align:middle line:90%
in cases such as yours.

00:50:24.565 --> 00:50:25.840 align:middle line:84%
And you don't have
to decide right now.

00:50:25.840 --> 00:50:27.970 align:middle line:84%
>> OK, if you can't help me,
that's something that I need

00:50:27.970 --> 00:50:28.770 align:middle line:90%
to know now.

00:50:28.770 --> 00:50:31.390 align:middle line:90%


00:50:31.390 --> 00:50:34.360 align:middle line:84%
>> Unfortunately, there is
no medication or treatment

00:50:34.360 --> 00:50:37.343 align:middle line:84%
on the market that can make
it go away immediately.

00:50:37.343 --> 00:50:41.780 align:middle line:90%


00:50:41.780 --> 00:50:45.231 align:middle line:90%
[PHONE RINGING]

00:50:45.231 --> 00:50:52.133 align:middle line:90%


00:50:52.133 --> 00:50:54.105 align:middle line:90%
[DOOR OPENING]

00:50:54.105 --> 00:50:58.634 align:middle line:90%
[DOOR CLOSING]

00:50:58.634 --> 00:50:59.434 align:middle line:90%
>> Hey.

00:50:59.434 --> 00:51:01.930 align:middle line:90%
Hey, excuse me.

00:51:01.930 --> 00:51:02.730 align:middle line:90%
Excuse me.

00:51:02.730 --> 00:51:03.530 align:middle line:90%
Hey!

00:51:03.530 --> 00:51:05.894 align:middle line:90%


00:51:05.894 --> 00:51:07.020 align:middle line:90%
Could you read this?

00:51:07.020 --> 00:51:07.480 align:middle line:90%
Could you read this?

00:51:07.480 --> 00:51:08.000 align:middle line:90%
>> Look.

00:51:08.000 --> 00:51:08.800 align:middle line:90%
Sorry, man.

00:51:08.800 --> 00:51:09.860 align:middle line:90%
I don't have the time.

00:51:09.860 --> 00:51:10.670 align:middle line:84%
>> OK, but can you
please just read-- buddy.

00:51:10.670 --> 00:51:12.086 align:middle line:84%
Buddy, can you
just do me a favor?

00:51:12.086 --> 00:51:13.413 align:middle line:90%
>> Stay away, man!

00:51:13.413 --> 00:51:30.130 align:middle line:90%


00:51:30.130 --> 00:51:31.700 align:middle line:90%
>> Good morning, Leah.

00:51:31.700 --> 00:51:32.680 align:middle line:90%
Come join us?

00:51:32.680 --> 00:51:39.050 align:middle line:90%


00:51:39.050 --> 00:51:41.000 align:middle line:84%
We decided to gather
here this morning

00:51:41.000 --> 00:51:43.790 align:middle line:84%
because it seemed to be
the most suitable place

00:51:43.790 --> 00:51:47.180 align:middle line:84%
to congratulate our new St.
Gabriel's Cancer Research

00:51:47.180 --> 00:51:53.150 align:middle line:90%
Institute fellow, Michael.

00:51:53.150 --> 00:51:54.910 align:middle line:84%
You have been
awarded St. Gabriel's

00:51:54.910 --> 00:51:56.064 align:middle line:90%
post-graduate fellowship.

00:51:56.064 --> 00:51:56.864 align:middle line:90%
Congratulations.

00:51:56.864 --> 00:51:59.620 align:middle line:90%
[APPLAUSE]

00:51:59.620 --> 00:52:00.420 align:middle line:90%


00:52:00.420 --> 00:52:02.840 align:middle line:90%
>> Excuse me.

00:52:02.840 --> 00:52:03.808 align:middle line:90%
My office.

00:52:03.808 --> 00:52:04.609 align:middle line:90%
>> Thank you.

00:52:04.609 --> 00:52:05.408 align:middle line:90%
>> Congrats.

00:52:05.408 --> 00:52:06.228 align:middle line:90%
>> Good job.

00:52:06.228 --> 00:52:07.028 align:middle line:90%
>> Thank you.

00:52:07.028 --> 00:52:08.032 align:middle line:90%
>> It's all you.

00:52:08.032 --> 00:52:09.520 align:middle line:90%
>> Congrats.

00:52:09.520 --> 00:52:25.392 align:middle line:90%


00:52:25.392 --> 00:52:27.410 align:middle line:90%
>> I'm sorry.

00:52:27.410 --> 00:52:29.116 align:middle line:90%
It was not up to me.

00:52:29.116 --> 00:52:32.074 align:middle line:90%
[INTERCOM]

00:52:32.074 --> 00:52:36.520 align:middle line:90%


00:52:36.520 --> 00:52:39.940 align:middle line:84%
>> A good friend of mine
is looking for a research

00:52:39.940 --> 00:52:42.550 align:middle line:90%
assistant.

00:52:42.550 --> 00:52:45.060 align:middle line:84%
Like you, he is currently
studying tumor immunotherapy

00:52:45.060 --> 00:52:46.120 align:middle line:90%
with stem cells.

00:52:46.120 --> 00:52:48.857 align:middle line:90%


00:52:48.857 --> 00:52:50.940 align:middle line:84%
He's an exceptional scientist
who could eventually

00:52:50.940 --> 00:52:54.240 align:middle line:90%
sponsor your own research.

00:52:54.240 --> 00:52:58.530 align:middle line:84%
The position doesn't pay much,
and he is based in Vancouver.

00:52:58.530 --> 00:53:01.870 align:middle line:90%
But I told him about you.

00:53:01.870 --> 00:53:04.579 align:middle line:84%
He is considering other
strong candidates.

00:53:04.579 --> 00:53:06.370 align:middle line:84%
But if you're willing
to drop out of school

00:53:06.370 --> 00:53:12.110 align:middle line:84%
and relocate immediately,
the position is yours.

00:53:12.110 --> 00:53:12.910 align:middle line:90%
I'm sorry.

00:53:12.910 --> 00:53:14.201 align:middle line:90%
This is the best that I can do.

00:53:14.201 --> 00:53:18.670 align:middle line:90%


00:53:18.670 --> 00:53:21.658 align:middle line:90%
[SPLASHING]

00:53:21.658 --> 00:53:37.594 align:middle line:90%


00:53:37.594 --> 00:53:41.080 align:middle line:90%
[GASPING]

00:53:41.080 --> 00:53:53.530 align:middle line:90%


00:53:53.530 --> 00:53:56.518 align:middle line:90%
[LIGHT CLICKING]

00:53:56.518 --> 00:53:57.514 align:middle line:90%


00:53:57.514 --> 00:53:58.510 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:53:58.510 --> 00:54:16.936 align:middle line:90%


00:54:16.936 --> 00:54:20.422 align:middle line:90%
[SPITS WATER]

00:54:20.422 --> 00:54:23.530 align:middle line:90%


00:54:23.530 --> 00:54:26.420 align:middle line:90%
>> I'm sorry.

00:54:26.420 --> 00:54:28.336 align:middle line:90%
I'd like to give hypnosis a try.

00:54:28.336 --> 00:54:34.180 align:middle line:90%


00:54:34.180 --> 00:54:37.690 align:middle line:84%
>> Just remember hypnosis
doesn't work for everyone.

00:54:37.690 --> 00:54:40.150 align:middle line:10%
And some people are able
to reach a deep place

00:54:40.150 --> 00:54:43.060 align:middle line:10%
of relaxation and
other people aren't.

00:54:43.060 --> 00:54:46.430 align:middle line:10%
So try not to let
your mind judge.

00:54:46.430 --> 00:54:49.820 align:middle line:84%
Just let yourself experience it,
and you can analyze everything

00:54:49.820 --> 00:54:50.660 align:middle line:90%
later.

00:54:50.660 --> 00:54:52.780 align:middle line:90%
Are you ready?

00:54:52.780 --> 00:54:53.580 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:54:53.580 --> 00:54:56.730 align:middle line:90%
>> OK, good.

00:54:56.730 --> 00:54:59.090 align:middle line:84%
Go ahead and just
close your eyes.

00:54:59.090 --> 00:55:01.730 align:middle line:90%


00:55:01.730 --> 00:55:04.690 align:middle line:84%
And we're going to start
with focusing on the breath,

00:55:04.690 --> 00:55:06.317 align:middle line:90%
just inhaling--

00:55:06.317 --> 00:55:07.780 align:middle line:90%
[INHALING]

00:55:07.780 --> 00:55:09.400 align:middle line:90%
>> --and exhaling.

00:55:09.400 --> 00:55:11.160 align:middle line:90%
[EXHALING]

00:55:11.160 --> 00:55:11.960 align:middle line:90%
>> That's it.

00:55:11.960 --> 00:55:14.058 align:middle line:90%
And inhale.

00:55:14.058 --> 00:55:16.398 align:middle line:90%
[INHALING]

00:55:16.398 --> 00:55:17.334 align:middle line:90%
>> And exhale.

00:55:17.334 --> 00:55:19.680 align:middle line:90%
[EXHALING]

00:55:19.680 --> 00:55:21.780 align:middle line:90%
>> You don't have to think.

00:55:21.780 --> 00:55:24.280 align:middle line:90%
You don't have to listen.

00:55:24.280 --> 00:55:26.220 align:middle line:10%
You don't have to do anything--

00:55:26.220 --> 00:55:27.030 align:middle line:10%
[EXHALING]

00:55:27.030 --> 00:55:32.664 align:middle line:84%
>> --except allow yourself to
lie on that couch feeling warm,

00:55:32.664 --> 00:55:35.918 align:middle line:90%
relaxed, and comfortable.

00:55:35.918 --> 00:55:38.850 align:middle line:90%


00:55:38.850 --> 00:55:43.590 align:middle line:84%
It's now time to begin
the journey backwards.

00:55:43.590 --> 00:55:47.620 align:middle line:10%
I want you to go back
to your childhood,

00:55:47.620 --> 00:55:52.040 align:middle line:10%
back to the time when
you were eight years old.

00:55:52.040 --> 00:55:55.460 align:middle line:84%
Whatever comes into
your mind is fine.

00:55:55.460 --> 00:55:58.760 align:middle line:90%
Just let yourself experience it.

00:55:58.760 --> 00:56:10.260 align:middle line:90%
Five, four, three, two, one.

00:56:10.260 --> 00:56:13.260 align:middle line:90%
[EXHALING]

00:56:13.260 --> 00:56:16.260 align:middle line:90%


00:56:16.260 --> 00:56:19.760 align:middle line:90%
>> What do you see?

00:56:19.760 --> 00:56:23.760 align:middle line:90%
[WIND BLOWING]

00:56:23.760 --> 00:56:27.260 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:56:27.260 --> 00:56:32.260 align:middle line:90%


