[HEARTBEAT]

00:56:35.260 --> 00:56:38.760 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:56:38.760 --> 00:56:42.260 align:middle line:90%


00:56:42.260 --> 00:56:45.260 align:middle line:90%
[WAVES CRASHING]

00:56:45.260 --> 00:56:51.760 align:middle line:90%


00:56:51.760 --> 00:56:52.760 align:middle line:90%
>> Where are you?

00:56:52.760 --> 00:56:55.760 align:middle line:90%


00:56:55.760 --> 00:56:58.760 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:56:58.760 --> 00:57:04.260 align:middle line:90%


00:57:04.260 --> 00:57:05.290 align:middle line:90%
>> In my room.

00:57:05.290 --> 00:57:08.218 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:57:08.218 --> 00:57:17.002 align:middle line:90%


00:57:17.002 --> 00:57:20.760 align:middle line:90%
[CHILD LAUGHING]

