>> What do you see?

00:57:21.560 --> 00:57:26.680 align:middle line:90%


00:57:26.680 --> 00:57:28.570 align:middle line:90%
>> My parents.

00:57:28.570 --> 00:57:29.450 align:middle line:90%
I miss them so much.

00:57:29.450 --> 00:57:30.700 align:middle line:90%
I wish they were here with me.

00:57:30.700 --> 00:57:33.550 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:57:33.550 --> 00:57:37.350 align:middle line:90%


00:57:37.350 --> 00:57:39.950 align:middle line:90%
>> I want you to go back now.

