[WIND BLOWING]

00:58:04.828 --> 00:58:07.732 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:58:07.732 --> 00:58:15.550 align:middle line:90%


00:58:15.550 --> 00:58:17.200 align:middle line:84%
>> Anything that
comes to your mind.

00:58:17.200 --> 00:58:21.691 align:middle line:90%


