[CLOCK TICKING]

00:58:40.660 --> 00:58:43.120 align:middle line:84%
>> --ended the
German government,

00:58:43.120 --> 00:58:47.790 align:middle line:84%
speaking that on this we
heard from them by 11 o'clock.

