[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:59:01.784 --> 00:59:05.070 align:middle line:90%


00:59:05.070 --> 00:59:08.100 align:middle line:90%
>> It's my house.

00:59:08.100 --> 00:59:10.540 align:middle line:90%
>> Can you see yourself?

